{"tid":715822,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開] 手機CPU(s835)對比notebook CPU(i7 8550u)測試","createTime":"2018-06-24T19:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T13:40:11.000Z","uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c587b9a7715e2e5a4c242a9ffba3890de13f348","tid":715822,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:17:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">平台</span><br />\nPC (唔知咩cpu): <br />\nArch Linux<br />\nblender 2.79<br />\n<br />\nNotebook (i7 8550u): <br />\nArch Linux<br />\nblender 2.79<br />\n<br />\nNote 8 (s835): <br />\nTermux <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.termux&amp;hl=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.termux%26hl%3Dzh_HK&d=qZBLZG8yiywiUcYiUXUpe4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8d9963d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.termux&amp;hl=zh_HK</a><br />\ndebian <a href=\"https://github.com/sp4rkie/debian-on-termux\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fsp4rkie%2Fdebian-on-termux&d=qZBLZG8yiywiUcYiUXUpe4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e1975ca7\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/sp4rkie/debian-on-termux</a><br />\nblender 2.78<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">方法</span><br />\nDownload &amp; unzip <a href=\"https://download.blender.org/demo/test/BMW27_2.blend.zip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdownload.blender.org%2Fdemo%2Ftest%2FBMW27_2.blend.zip&d=qZBLZG8yiywiUcYiUXUpe4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b98b5aab\" target=\"_blank\">https://download.blender.org/demo/test/BMW27_2.blend.zip</a><br />\n行句command, <code>$ blender -b bmw27_cpu.blend -x 1 -o //render -f 0</code><br />\n<br />\n就係用note 8畫呢張圖出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://transfer.sh/CtTKg/a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransfer.sh%2FCtTKg%2Fa.png&h=712418f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">偏差</span><br />\nPC頻率穩定<br />\n8550u 頭幾十秒係3.xGHz，之後穩定係2.6Ghz，粗略當2.65Ghz計<br />\ns835 頭big core頭幾分鐘係2.36GHz，不斷drop並穩定至1.34GHz，粗略當1.38Ghz計。Little core穩定係1.9Ghz<br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/b01c3360e2c6ad004471c18b397cf80e84c229bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2Fb01c3360e2c6ad004471c18b397cf80e84c229bc.jpg&h=b6b8c3af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結果</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/ccb73be01ec86daac936fee0088b4e320d2b0392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2Fccb73be01ec86daac936fee0088b4e320d2b0392.jpg&h=dfab0987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://drop.wtako.net/file/aa4c2107bcb849e6676246182e7c56005894862d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.wtako.net%2Ffile%2Faa4c2107bcb849e6676246182e7c56005894862d.jpg&h=bf31499b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3539c4a932f3de7a6d1a99e6e7a87ac8cb8d9527","tid":715822,"uid":658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:40:25.000Z","msg":"依家又出一粒1000代號既cpu 專for notebook用<br />\n核心面積都比850大，頻率好似boot 到4ghz <br />\n其實整粒Intel+arm既機唔得咩，待機後台處理用arm <br />\nhigh performance 用intel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5916b250d98910cb836d35a40d61c36487662b3","tid":715822,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3539c4a932f3de7a6d1a99e6e7a87ac8cb8d9527","tid":715822,"uid":658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:40:25.000Z","msg":"依家又出一粒1000代號既cpu 專for notebook用<br />\n核心面積都比850大，頻率好似boot 到4ghz <br />\n其實整粒Intel+arm既機唔得咩，待機後台處理用arm <br />\nhigh performance 用intel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:15:53.000Z","msg":"x86 + arm對於os黎講應該好難，但一般u + 7y一定得，係intel唔肯整<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif